UNITED STATES of America, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Wei M. SHI, Defendant-Appellant. No. 02-2241. United States Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. March 13, 2003.

Before BAUER, POSNER, and ROVNER, Circuit Judges.

ORDER

On consideration of the petition for rehearing filed on March 4, 2003 by plaintiff-appellee. All of the judges on the panel have voted to deny the petition. The petition is therefore DENIED.
